description: Minimal diffs, comments, and helpers; Vue/shared conventions
alwaysApply: true
---

# Code style

- Smallest correct diff; no unrelated refactors.
- Comments only for non-obvious business logic; `//` not block comments.
- Helpers only when reused (DRY); no single-use helpers.
- Vue: `<script setup lang="ts">`, relative imports with `.js` extension.
- Prefer existing composables and shared UI (`PanelShell`, `HpBar`, `BoardCell`, …).
- Design tokens from `packages/client/src/style.css` (`var(--color-*)`).
- Game logic in `@vtt-core/shared`; both backends call the same shared functions.
